<h3>Where Things Are:</h3>

<ul>
  <li> <code>PIA_DIR = &piaDIR; </code>
       (parent of src, Doc, etc.) <br>
       If things are set up correctly, this should also be reachable as
       <a href="/PIA/">/PIA/</a>
  <li> <code>PIA_LIB = <get pia name="main::PIA_LIB"></code>
       (agency libraries)
  <li> <code>PIA_ROOT= <get pia name="main::PIA_ROOT"></code>
       (agent interforms)
  <li> <code>USR_DIR = <get pia name="main::USR_DIR"></code>
       (your customizations and agent output)  <br>
       If things are set up correctly, this should also be reachable as
       <a href="/My/">/My/</a>
  <li> <code>USR_ROOT= <get pia name="main::USR_ROOT"></code>
       (your customized interforms)
</ul>

